Well, i-it all happened rather quickly. I mean, I... I, uh...

378
00:27:31,579 --> 00:27:33,790
她严厉吗？她会发号施令吗？
Will she be firm? Will she give commands?

379
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:37,336
她能塑造孩子们吗？
Will she mould our young breed?

380
00:27:37,586 --> 00:27:41,090
