perhaps you'd better tell Ellen to dismiss the others.

383
00:27:46,847 --> 00:27:51,268
其他人？哦，是的，艾伦？
是的，先生？
The others? Oh, yes. Ellen?
Y-Yes, sir?

384
00:27:51,519 --> 00:27:54,481
