你的包真滑稽
是地毯
That's a funny sort of bag.
Carpet.

391
00:28:22,888 --> 00:28:24,807
你是说包里装的是地毯吗？
不，是用地毯做的
You mean to carry carpets in?
No. Made of.

392
00:28:25,057 --> 00:28:29,229
这是你的房间，从这里可以欣赏到公园
This is your room, and there's a lovely view of the park.

393
00:28:29,479 --> 00:28:32,065
嗯
Hmm.

394
00:28:32,316 --> 00:28:36,279
好吧，毕竟不是白金汉宫
Well, it's not exactly Buckingham Palace.

395
00:28:37,739 --> 00:28:40,534
还挺干净
Still, it's clean.

396
00:28:40,784 --> 00:28:43,203
我觉得它很合适
Yes, I think it will be quite suitable.

397
