只是到处需要整理一下
Just needs a touch here and there.

398
00:28:46,999 --> 00:28:49,210
首先，就像我常说的那样
Well, first things first.

399
00:28:49,461 --> 00:28:54,800
挂帽子最合适的地方就是衣帽架
I always say, the place to hang a hat is on a hat stand.

400
00:29:07,940 --> 00:29:12,404
哈！这怎么能用呢？
Ah! This will never do!

401
00:29:16,617 --> 00:29:21,039
我更喜欢大一点的
I much prefer seeing all of my face at the same time.

402
00:29:21,289 --> 00:29:23,792
但是里面是空的呀！
There... But there was nothing in it.

403
00:29:24,042 --> 00:29:26,962
不要根据表面现象作判断
Never judge things by their appearance.

404
00:29:27,212 --> 00:29:31,300
即使是一只地毯包。我就从来没有
Even carpetbags. I'm sure I never do.

405
00:29:35,889 --> 00:29:40,561
美丽的东西永远是快乐的
A thing of beauty is a joy forever.

406
00:29:43,731 --> 00:29:48,487
