轮到你了，简
Now you, Jane.

423
00:31:04,199 --> 00:31:08,829
嗯，“爱傻笑，不把东西放好”
Mmm. "Rather inclined to giggle. Doesn't put things away."

424
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:11,499
