Here, here, half a mo.
Leave her alone! Leave my sister alone!

1256
01:36:56,888 --> 01:37:00,809
嘿，没事的，你们的老朋友不会伤害你的
Easy, now. Your old friend ain't gonna hurt ya.

1257
01:37:01,434 --> 01:37:03,144
伯特，是你啊！
Bert, it's you!

1258
01:37:03,394 --> 01:37:06,815
正是在下，听从你的吩咐
In the flesh, and at your service.

1259
01:37:07,065 --> 01:37:10,818
你可真脏！
哦，也许是有一两处污渍
You're filthy!
Oh, perhaps a smudge or two.

1260
01:37:11,069 --> 01:37:13,238
碰巧今天我是个扫烟囱的人
It so happens that today I'm a chimney sweep.

1261
01:37:13,488 --> 01:37:15,698
哦，伯特，我们吓得要命
Oh, Bert, we're so frightened.

1262
01:37:15,949 --> 01:37:18,076
好了，好了，现在不用害怕
Now, now, don't take on so.

1263
01:37:18,326 --> 01:37:21,120
伯特会向你们的父亲那样照顾好你们的
Bert'll take care of you like I was your own father.

1264
01:37:21,371 --> 01:37:23,414
谁在追你们？
我们的父亲……
Now, who's after you?
Father is.

1265
01:37:23,665 --> 01:37:26,584
什么？
他带我们去他的银行参观
What?
He brought us to see his bank.

1266
01:37:26,834 --> 01:37:29,921
我不知道我们做了什么，但一定是非常糟糕的事情
I don't know what we did, but it must've been something dreadful.

1267
01:37:30,171 --> 01:37:33,299
他让警察追我们，还有军队，所有人都在追我们
He sent the police after us, and the Army and everything.

1268
01:37:33,549 --> 01:37:35,343
迈克尔，别这么夸张
Michael, don't exaggerate.

1269
01:37:35,593 --> 01:37:38,346
好吧，一定有什么误会
Well, now, there must be some mistake.

1270
01:37:38,596 --> 01:37:40,682
你们的爸爸是个好人，他爱你们
Your dad's a fine gentleman and he loves ya!

1271
01:37:40,932 --> 01:37:44,727
不可不这样认为。你最好能看见他当时的那张脸
I don't think so. You should've seen the look on his face.

1272
01:37:44,977 --> 01:37:46,688
他压根就不喜欢我们
He doesn't like us at all.

1273
01:37:46,938 --> 01:37:49,857
好了，别好像好像的，好吗？
Well, now that don't seem likely, does it?

1274
01:37:50,108 --> 01:37:53,152
这是事实
It's true.

1275
01:37:53,403 --> 01:37:55,196
让我们坐一坐
Let's sit down.

1276
01:37:55,446 --> 01:37:57,949
你知道，……
You know, begging your pardon...

1277
01:37:58,199 --> 01:38:01,244
我很同情你们的父亲
but the one my heart goes out to is your father.

1278
01:38:01,494 --> 01:38:05,331
他在那个冷酷的，无情的银行中日复一日地……
There he is in that cold, heartless bank day after day...

1279
01:38:05,581 --> 01:38:09,168
被一大堆冰冷的，无感情的金钱所包围
hemmed in by mounds of cold, heartless money.

1280
01:38:09,418 --> 01:38:11,087
我不喜欢看到任何生命被关在笼中
I don't like to see any living thing caged up.

1281
01:38:11,337 --> 01:38:13,840
父亲被关在笼子里了？
Father in a cage?

1282
01:38:14,090 --> 01:38:16,968
笼子的尺寸和形状不同而已，你知道
They makes cages in all sizes and shapes, you know.

1283
01:38:17,218 --> 01:38:19,053
一些是银行形状的，用地毯什么的来制作
Bank-shaped some of 'em, carpets and all.

1284
01:38:19,303 --> 01:38:22,265
父亲没有麻烦，我们有！
Father's not in trouble. We are.

1285
01:38:22,515 --> 01:38:25,518
哦，你们确信？
Oh, sure about that, are you?

1286
01:38:25,768 --> 01:38:29,188
换个角度想想，你们有你们的母亲照顾你们
Look at it this way. You've got your mother to look after you.

1287
01:38:29,438 --> 01:38:33,150
还有玛丽?泼平斯，琼斯警察，还有我
And Mary Poppins, and Constable Jones and me.

1288
01:38:33,401 --> 01:38:36,112
谁来照顾你们的父亲呢？你们说说看
Who looks after your father? Tell me that.

1289
01:38:36,362 --> 01:38:39,073
当一些可怕的事情发生时，他该怎么办？
When something terrible happens, what does he do?

1290
01:38:39,323 --> 01:38:41,325
他只能自己照顾自己
Fends for himself, he does.

1291
01:38:41,575 --> 01:38:44,453
他向谁倾诉？没人！
Who does he tell about it? No one!

1292
01:38:44,704 --> 01:38:46,664
不能在家里倾诉他的烦心事
Don't blab his troubles at home.

1293
01:38:46,914 --> 01:38:51,335
他只是毫无怨言，独自一人，安静地努力承受着
He just pushes on at his job, uncomplaining and alone and silent.

1294
01:38:51,585 --> 01:38:55,548
他并不是很安静！
迈克尔，安静点
He's not very silent!
Michael, be quiet.

1295
01:38:55,798 --> 01:38:59,593
伯特，你确定父亲真的需要我们的帮助吗？
Bert, do you think Father really needs our help?

1296
01:38:59,844 --> 01:39:02,596
呃，这个我不该说的
Well, not my place to say.

1297
01:39:02,847 --> 01:39:06,433
我只注意到，一个父亲常常需要那么一点帮助
I only observe that a father can always do with a bit of help.

1298
01:39:06,684 --> 01:39:10,563
来吧，我带你们回家
Come on, I'll take you home.

1299
01:39:16,819 --> 01:39:19,905
黑烟囱……冒黑烟……
Chim chiminy, chim chiminy
Chim chim cheree

1300
01:39:20,155 --> 01:39:23,450
一个扫烟囱人就是幸运星
A sweep is as lucky as lucky can be

1301
01:39:23,701 --> 01:39:26,662
黑烟囱……冒黑烟……
Chim chiminy, chim chiminy
Chim chim cheroo

1302
01:39:26,912 --> 01:39:30,082
当我和你握手，好运就会传染给你
Good luck will rub off when I shakes hands with you

1303
01:39:30,332 --> 01:39:33,585
或者和我接吻
Or blow me a kiss

1304
01:39:33,836 --> 01:39:37,923
好运也会传染给你
And that's lucky too

1305
01:39:38,299 --> 01:39:41,260
当生活就想一串梯子
Now as the ladder of life has been strung

1306
01:39:41,510 --> 01:39:44,680
你可以想想在梯子最底端的扫烟囱人
You might think a sweep's on the bottommost rung

1307
01:39:44,930 --> 01:39:48,058
虽然我成天跟炉灰打交道
Though I spends me time in the ashes and smoke

1308
01:39:48,308 --> 01:39:51,729
但在这整个广袤的世界里，没有其它家伙能比我更快乐
In this whole wide world there's no happier bloke

1309
01:39:51,979 --> 01:39:54,857
