噢，艾伦，去看看是谁，把他们打发走
Oh, Ellen, see who that is, and send them away.

1318
01:40:26,430 --> 01:40:29,057
我已经迟到了！
是的，夫人
I'm dreadfully late!
Yes, ma'am.

1319
01:40:29,308 --> 01:40:32,352
好了，我现在可以离开了。
哦别，请陪我们到父亲回家来为止吧。
Well, I'll be gettin' along now.
Oh, please stay till Father comes home.

1320
01:40:32,603 --> 01:40:37,024
如果你跟他握手，他会感觉好多的。
He'll feel much better if you shake hands with him.

1321
01:40:37,274 --> 01:40:40,652
是孩子们
我想他们应该跟他们的父亲在一起
It's the children, ma'am.
Oh, I thought they were with their father.

1322
01:40:40,902 --> 01:40:43,864
你们不是又逃跑了吧？你们知道这会让我多痛苦吗？
You haven't been running off again, have you? You know how terribly it upsets me.

1323
01:40:44,114 --> 01:40:46,033
哦夫人，准确地讲他们并不是逃跑
Oh, they haven't exactly been running away, ma'am.

1324
01:40:46,283 --> 01:40:48,577
然而，他们受了点惊吓，需要有人照顾
They have had bit of a fright, though. Need someone to look after 'em.

1325
01:40:48,827 --> 01:40:52,622
哦，当然！玛丽?泼平斯会照顾他们的
Oh, of course! Mary Poppins will.

1326
01:40:52,873 --> 01:40:55,167
噢，不，今天她休假
Oh, no, it's her day off!

1327
01:40:55,417 --> 01:40:59,629
艾伦，我想请你……
不行，夫人，我自己的活还没有干完呢
Ellen, I wonder if you would...
No, ma'am. I haven't done me brasses yet.

1328
01:40:59,880 --> 01:41:02,716
好吧，你能问一下布里夫人吗？
就算给我一百英镑，我也不干，夫人
Well, will you ask Mrs Brill?
Not for a hundred quid, ma'am.

1329
01:41:02,966 --> 01:41:08,263
今天是烘焙日，你知道要煮多少东西么！
This here is baking day, and you know how Cook is!

1330
01:41:08,346 --> 01:41:09,890
你怎么样，先生？
What about you, sir?

1331
01:41:10,140 --> 01:41:12,559
你刚才已经非常热心地照顾这些孩子了
You've been so kind in looking after the children.

1332
01:41:12,809 --> 01:41:15,103
唔……我吗？夫人，我……我不得不离开
Wh... Uh, me, ma'am? W-Well, well, l-l-I have to be moving along.

1333
01:41:15,353 --> 01:41:17,105
市长大人家的烟囱被堵住了
The Lord Mayor's got a stopped-up chimney.

1334
01:41:17,355 --> 01:41:19,900
烟囱，你可真聪明
Chimney. How clever of you to know.

1335
01:41:20,150 --> 01:41:25,447
我们客厅的烟囱糟糕透了。烟不断地往客厅冒
Our drawing room chimney's in the most ghastly condition. Smokes incessantly.

1336
01:41:25,697 --> 01:41:27,240
唔……
非常谢谢！
W-W...
Thank you so much!

1337
01:41:27,490 --> 01:41:31,953
但，但是……
还有，顺便带好孩子
But...
Besides, it'll amuse the children.

1338
01:41:32,203 --> 01:41:33,997
市长大人家的马上就要剧烈地喷发了
The Lord Mayor's gonna be terrible put out.

1339
01:41:34,247 --> 01:41:36,958
哦，谢谢你，我会非常感激的
Oh, thank you so much. I do appreciate it.

1340
01:41:37,208 --> 01:41:43,089
我必须得走了。我们勇敢的姐妹在监狱中正等着我领她们唱歌呢！
I must hurry. Our gallant ladies in prison are waiting for me to lead them in song!

1341
01:41:43,340 --> 01:41:47,594
再见，亲爱的，一会儿见
Goodbye, my darlings. See you soon.

1342
01:41:52,891 --> 01:41:56,227
我骄傲地挑选猪鬃工具，是的，我骄傲
I choose me bristles with pride, yes, I do

1343
01:41:56,478 --> 01:42:01,858
扫帚用来扫烟囱，用刷子来通烟道
A broom for the shaft and a brush for the flue

1344
01:42:02,108 --> 01:42:05,111
这里很黑很暗
Oh, it's awfully dark and gloomy up there.

1345
01:42:05,361 --> 01:42:08,114
现在，你将知道你的看法是错误的
There now. You see how wrong people can be?

1346
01:42:08,364 --> 01:42:13,203
这儿是通向你所谓魔法世界的一条通道
That there is what you might call a doorway to a place of enchantment.

1347
01:42:13,453 --> 01:42:18,124
在上面烟雾如巨浪般翻滚，卷曲
Up where the smoke is all billowed and curled

1348
01:42:18,374 --> 01:42:21,044
在星星和地面之间
'Tween pavement and stars

1349
01:42:21,294 --> 01:42:25,215
是扫烟囱人的世界
Is the chimney sweep world

1350
01:42:25,215 --> 01:42:27,717
这里几乎没有白天
When there's hardly no day

1351
01:42:27,967 --> 01:42:30,803
也几乎没有黑夜
Nor hardly no night

1352
01:42:31,054 --> 01:42:35,058
所有的事物一半在阴影里
There's things half in shadow

1353
01:42:35,308 --> 01:42:38,353
一半在光线下
And halfway in light

1354
01:42:38,603 --> 01:42:43,983
站在伦敦的屋顶
On the rooftops of London

1355
01:42:44,233 --> 01:42:47,320
视野真开阔
Coo, what a sight.

1356
01:42:47,570 --> 01:42:49,864
我真希望我们能到上面去
I do wish we could go up there.

1357
01:42:50,114 --> 01:42:52,158
我也是！我喜欢烟囱
So do I! I like chimneys.

1358
01:42:52,408 --> 01:42:57,205
非常正确！烟囱是一件完美的东西
Oh, rightly so! A chimney is a wondrous thing.

1359
01:42:57,455 --> 01:42:59,707
她高高地建在屋顶上
She's built tall right up there on the roof.

1360
01:42:59,957 --> 01:43:03,211
当风向正确的时候，风吹过她的顶端
When the wind is just right, it blows across her top...

1361
01:43:03,461 --> 01:43:05,963
驱动烟从烟道中穿过
then draws the smoke right up the flue.

1362
01:43:06,214 --> 01:43:09,842
拿着，用刷子感受一下底部的吸力
Here. Feel the pull on the end of that brush.

1363
01:43:10,092 --> 01:43:12,553
这就好像站在鲸鱼喷水口的底部
It's like I got a whale on the end of the line, ain't it?

1364
01:43:12,804 --> 01:43:18,100
迈克尔，小心，你永远不知道站在壁炉旁边会发生什么事情
Michael, be careful. You never know what may happen around a fireplace.

1365
01:43:18,809 --> 01:43:22,271
天啦！
Oh, bother!

1366
01:43:23,439 --> 01:43:27,735
迈克尔，迈克尔，下来！
Michael! Michael, come back down here.

1367
01:43:27,985 --> 01:43:30,196
迈克尔，你在哪里？
Michael! Michael, where are you?

1368
01:43:30,446 --> 01:43:31,697
好吧，我不得不说，这有点尴尬！
Well, that's a bit awkward. I must say!

1369
01:43:31,948 --> 01:43:36,202
伯特，麻烦你不要出馊主意了！
Bert, I'll thank you to stop putting ideas in their heads!

1370
01:43:36,702 --> 01:43:38,704
现在轮到下一个
我能跟在后面么？
There goes the other one.
Shall I go after 'em?

1371
01:43:38,955 --> 01:43:42,833
我们不能让他们像袋鼠一样在上面闲逛，对吧？
Well, we can't have them gallivanting up there like kangaroos, can we?

1372
01:43:43,084 --> 01:43:47,296
迈克尔，别害怕。事情正在……
Michael, don't be frightened. Everything's going...

1373
01:43:52,843 --> 01:43:56,305
你能立刻把你的东西放下吗？
Will you put your things on at once?

1374
01:43:58,307 --> 01:44:00,226
请快一点
Hurry up, please. Spit spot!

1375
01:44:00,476 --> 01:44:03,729
你在这儿！我以为你丢下我们了。
我们没有这个意思
Here you are! I thought you'd left us.
We didn't mean to.

1376
01:44:03,979 --> 01:44:06,524
真好，一切平安无事。事实上……
Well, no harm done. The truth is...

1377
01:44:06,774 --> 01:44:10,236
这是你们所说的偶发事件
this is what you might call a fortuitous circumstance.

1378
01:44:10,486 --> 01:44:12,071
看那儿
Look there.

1379
01:44:12,321 --> 01:44:17,493
一个茂密的雨林正等着我们去探索
A trackless jungle just waiting to be explored.

1380
01:44:17,743 --> 01:44:21,997
为什么不行，玛丽?泼平斯？
求求你了，玛丽?泼平斯
Why not, Mary Poppins?
Oh, please, Mary Poppins?
Please!

1381
01:44:21,997 --> 01:44:27,086
好吧，如果这是必要的
Oh, well. If we must, we must.

1382
01:44:30,339 --> 01:44:31,257
同意
Fall in.

1383
01:44:31,507 --> 01:44:34,718
精神点，精神点。跟上！跟上！
Look lively, look lively. Jump to it! Jump to it!

1384
01:44:34,969 --> 01:44:38,764
排成一列，立正！
Get in line. Attention!

1385
01:44:39,014 --> 01:44:41,892
扛枪！
A-show arms!

1386
01:44:42,142 --> 01:44:46,689
向右转！
A-right turn!

1387
01:44:51,777 --> 01:44:56,573
齐步走！
Quick march!

1388
01:45:23,225 --> 01:45:26,937
喂，那儿！
Hello there!

1389
01:45:29,940 --> 01:45:33,735
很好，擦干净，迈克尔
It's just good, clean soot, Michael.

1390
01:45:38,323 --> 01:45:42,786
我们只能走到这里了，是吗？
当然不
As far as we go, right?
Not at all.

1391
01:46:30,959 --> 01:46:36,047
我说什么来着？整个世界都在你脚下
What did I tell ya? There's the whole world at your feet.

1392
01:46:36,298 --> 01:46:42,220
只有鸟儿、星星和扫烟囱人见过
And who gets to see it, but the birds, the stars and the chimney sweeps?

1393
01:46:51,688 --> 01:46:54,274
真棒，但我们必须走出这片夜色
Quite nice, but we should all get in out of the night air.

1394
01:46:54,524 --> 01:46:58,403
请跟我来
Follow me, please.

1395
01:47:06,494 --> 01:47:10,457
黑烟囱……冒黑烟……
Chim chiminy, chim chiminy
Chim chim cheree

1396
01:47:10,707 --> 01:47:14,752
当你和一个扫烟囱人在一起，就如同与欢乐在一起
When you're with a sweep you're in glad company

1397
01:47:15,003 --> 01:47:18,631
哪儿都不如一群快乐的人群
Nowhere is there a more happier crew

1398
01:47:18,882 --> 01:47:22,844
他们都这样唱着
Then them what sings chim chim cheree, chim cheroo

1399
01:47:23,094 --> 01:47:25,763
黑烟囱……冒黑烟……
Chim chiminy chim chim

1400
01:47:26,014 --> 01:47:30,310
冒黑烟……
Cheree chim cheroo

1401
01:47:30,560 --> 01:47:33,313
- Cheroo!

1402
01:47:33,563 --> 01:47:36,107
- Cheroo!

1403
01:47:36,357 --> 01:47:38,610
这些都是我的哥们！
It's all me pals!

1404
01:47:38,860 --> 01:47:41,112
来跳舞！
Step in time!

1405
01:47:41,362 --> 01:47:44,574
来跳舞！
Step in time!

1406
01:47:44,824 --> 01:47:46,159
来跳舞！
Step in time!

